This project analyzes survey responses from computer science students regarding their academic experiences, mental health, and productivity **before**, **during**, and **after the COVID-19 pandemic**.

It supports:
- ğŸŸ¦ Likert-scale analysis (e.g., "Strongly Agree" â†’ numeric)
