## ğŸ§  Key Features

- Automatically deduplicates repeated survey questions
- Recognizes Likert-style responses (e.g., "1 - Never", "5 - Strongly agree")
- Detects text questions based on their **instructions** in the question text (e.g., â€œYou can answer in full sentences...â€)
- Creates visualizations using `seaborn` and saves them to `plots/`
- Exports all text-based responses into a human-readable `.txt` file

