## âœ… Setup Instructions

```bash
# 1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/gendiv-survey-analysis.git
cd gendiv-survey-analysis

# 2. Create and activate the environment using environment.yml
conda env create -f environment.yml
conda activate gendiv

# 3. Run the analysis script
python scripts/survey_visualization.py
```